      "text": "BREACH AND CLEAR Voidship’s Company – Battle Tactic Stratagem IMPERIAL NAVY BREACHERS roll Wound roll Your , just after an unit from yourarmy opens a That unit. Until the end of the turn, each time a model in your unit makes an attack, if that model is on the opposite side of the Hatchway from the side it started the turn on, add 1 to the and add 1 to the AMMO RATIONS Voidship’s Company – Battle Tactic Stratagem VOIDFARERS Start of your One or more units from your army. Select one enemy unit. Until the end of the phase, each time a model in one of your units makes an attack that targets that enemy unit, improve the Armour Penetration characteristic of that attack by 1. BOARDING DRILL Voidship’s Company – Strategic Ploy Stratagem VOIDFARERS Fell Back Start of your unit from your army. Until the end of the phase, your unit is eligible to shoot or perform a in a turn in which it SHIP’S WATCH Voidship’s Company – Strategic Ploy Stratagem roll Critical Your opponent's Up to two units from your army that have not fired this phase. Until the end of the phase, each time a model in one of your units makes an attack while firing Overwatch, an unmodified of 5+ is required to score a hit, instead of an unmodified 6. When doing so, models in your units can ignore other models in their unit for the purposes of , and each time a model in one of your units makes an attack, if that unit contains a Canid model, a successful unmodified Hit roll of 5+ scores a [Interdiction Team] Whether boarding a vessel smuggling unsanctioned psyker-mutants, eliminating the unholy allies of some corrupt Planetary Governor, or moving swiftly to snatch proscribed interstellar contraband, Adeptus Arbites Interdiction Teams handle the most perilous of void crimes with extreme prejudice. [Mustering a Boarding Patrol] INQUISITOR You can include up to two of the following unit: You can include up to three of each of the following units: You can include up to one of the following unit: If you include an model, you can include one of the following unit: [Forming Boarding Squads] [Rules Adaptations] [Army Rule] [Imperial Insights] Assigned Agents Normal move Units from your army with the ability replace that ability with this one. Each time this unit performs the Tactical Manoeuvre, the you select for that Tactical Manoeuvre is immediately by your army, instead of at the start of your next . This unit can then make a of up to D6\" (but is still not eligible to shoot or this turn). [Detachment Rule] [Chastisor Auto-Vox] ADEPTUS ARBITES Battle-shock test Below Half-strength Battle-shock tests In your opponent’s , each enemy unit within 3\" of one or more units from your army must take a . If that enemy unit is also , subtract 1 from that test. This Detachment rule cannot cause a unit to take two in the same phase."
