      "name": "Enhancements",
      "text": "{'table': [['Predestined Champion Many strands of fate intertwine about this Champion of Tzeentch, for it has been foretold that he may achieve greatness. Of course, fate is ever fickle... While the bearer is on the battlefield, you are considered to control one additional objective marker for the purposes of the Twisting Fate army rule.']]} {'table': [['Astral Predation With a great psychic effort, this warrior savant projects his eldritch soul out from his mortal shell that it might pass through doorways into other futures and strike down his enemies before they have a chance to react. Once per battle, in your Movement phase , when the bearer is selected to move, it can use this Enhancement. If it does, select one closed Hatchway on the battlefield. Until the end of the phase, the bearer can move through that Hatchway as if it was open (note that this does not open that Hatchway - it remains closed).']]}"
